e9d755b39de.mp4?t=1666906233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>夺回人类设施，捣毁僵尸巢穴，恢复人类统治：这个世界里还留存着不少可以利用的人类设施，夺回他们可以帮助你更好的生存，捣毁僵尸巢穴可以帮助你进一步的巩固胜利成果。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/764920/extras/4466126e4f380a6810aa95a44892e80f.avif?t=1666906233\" width=638 height=250 /></span><br>骇客机械文明：这个世界残存着末世前人类科技文明用来对抗僵尸的终极武器——UA机器人，想办法倾入它们的系统，控制它们，它们将成为你最好的生存工具。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/764920/extras/7a537dccad9e71f54773a111c9691f6f.poster.avif?t=1666906233\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/764920/extras/7a537dccad9e71f54773a111c9691f6f.webm?t=1666906233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/764920/extras/7a537dccad9e71f54773a111c9691f6f.mp4?t=1666906233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>基础生存要素：你要吃饱，你要喝足，你要避免感染，你要通过烹饪来获得更好的回复效果，活着才是真谛。",
